<iframe src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=oilfilter.htm&amp;send=false&amp;layout=standard&amp;width=250&amp;show_faces=false&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;font&amp;height=35" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:250px; height:35px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
<h1>K&amp;N Oil Filters for Automotive Applications</h1>
<table width="980" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    <tr>
      <td><h2>Automotive Premium Wrench-Off Canister Oil Filters</h2>
<div style="float:right; padding:10px; width:386px; text-align:center;"><img src="images/oil_filter_boxes.jpg" width="300" height="259" alt="Automotive Premium Canister Oil Filters" /><br />K&amp;N Automotive Wrench-Off Canister Oil Filters</div><h3>Oil Filters for Cars, Trucks, SUV and more!</h3>
				  K&amp;N's premium wrench-off line of automotive and marine 
				  canister oil filters were developed to meet the high 
				  performance demands of race applications. They have rapidly 
				  become popular for their canister strength and durability. 
				  These canister style oil filters are designed to handle higher 
				  oil pressures than a standard oil filter and can be used with 
				  the latest synthetic motor oils. Most of these premium automotive and marine canister oil filters come with a 
				  1 inch welded nut on the top that makes removal easy. [ 
				  <a href="wrenchoff_oilfilter.htm">MORE</a> ]
<ul>
<li>Premium canister oil filters for car, truck, and SUV applications</li>
<li>Exposed nut designed for easy removal (where applicable)</li>
<li>Heavy duty construction, high flow rates, &amp; outstanding oil filtration</li>
<li>Traps 99% of harmful contaminants</li>
<li>Can be used with the latest synthetic motor oils</li>
</ul>
<img src="/images/img/wrench-off.jpg"></td>
  </tr>
            <tr><td><hr /></td></tr>
            <tr>
           	  <td><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
              <tr>
              <td colspan="3"><h2>K&amp;N Pro Series Premium Oil Filters</h2></td>
              </tr>
              <tr><td colspan="3">&nbsp;</td></tr>
              <tr><td width="386"><p align="center"><img src="images/pro-series-filters-with-box.jpg" alt="Pro Series Canister Oil Filters" width="245" height="250" /><br />K&amp;N Pro Series Canister Oil Filters</p></td>
              <td width="10"></td>
              <td><h3>Pro Series Canister Automotive Oil Filters</h3>
K&amp;N Pro Series Oil Filters have been specially designed for professional installers and service providers. Their high flow design can help to improve engine performance by reducing oil filter restriction. Our Pro Series Oil Filters have a fluted canister shape so they can be removed with a traditional oil filter wrench commonly available to commercial installers. These Pro Series oil filters provide outstanding filtration and engine protection throughout their service life. They are engineered to handle all grades of synthetic, conventional and blended motor oils. The pleated media provides high capacity making them suitable for extended oil change intervals when used in accordance with the vehicle and motor oil manufacturers recommendation. K&amp;N Pro Series Oil Filters are available for canister and cartridge type oil filter applications.&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>High-Flow / Low Restriction Design</li>
	<li>Rolled Threads</li>
	<li>Fluted shape for traditional oil filter wrenches</li>
	<li>Anti-drainback valves (where applicable) PSI relief valves (where 
	applicable)</li>
</ul></td>
              </tr>
              
              </table></td>
            </tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
            <tr><td><hr /></td></tr>
            <tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
            <tr><td><h2>Automotive Cartridge Oil Filters</h2><div style="float:right; padding:10px; width:386px; text-align:center;"><img src="images/cartridge_oilfilters.jpg" alt="Pro Series Cartridge Oil Filters" width="250" height="233" /><br />
					K&amp;N Cartridge Oil Filters</div>
<h3>Cartridge Oil Filters for Cars, Trucks, SUVs and more!</h3>
				K&amp;N's line of automotive cartridge oil filters provide 
				outstanding filtration. Their high flow design can help to 
				improve engine performance by reducing oil filter restriction. 
				They are also ideal for high-end synthetic motor oils.
<ul>
<li>Cartridge oil filters for cars, trucks, SUV's and other applications</li>
<li>Great with synthetic or conventional motor oils</li>
	<li>High flow rates &amp; outstanding oil filtration</li>
	<li>Traps 99% of harmful contaminants</li>
</ul><br /></td></tr>
<tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
            <tr><td><hr /></td></tr>
            
             <tr>
           	  <td><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
              <tr><td colspan="3"><h2>K&amp;N Washable / Reusable Billet Oil Filters</h2></td>
              </tr>
              <tr><td colspan="3">&nbsp;</td></tr>
              <tr>
                  <td width="584"><h3>Our Best and Highest Flowing Oil Filters</h3> 
K&amp;N is proud to release a new reusable oil filter that will last the lifetime of your vehicle under normal vehicle operating conditions. The filter housing, bypass valve and call plate are CNC machined from Billet 6061 T6 Aluminum. The filter cartridge uses stainless steel micro-screen and end caps bonded into a single piece for extra durability. The mechanical filtration is accomplished with dual woven T 304 stainless steel micro-screen that provides excellent engine protection while providing substantial increase in oil flow when compared to standard disposable oil filters. The filter cartridge contains two Neodymium magnets located in the filter screens for additional capacity and debris removal. All of the seals are dependable long lasting mil-spec Viton for a dependable seal. The billet by-pass valve is removable for cleaning and uses a stainless steel sealing ball with a stainless steel spring for increased service life. Each oil filter is manufactured from high quality material and components, designed for very high flow rates at low restriction, provides excellent engine protection and is easy to clean and maintain.  A K&amp;N Reusable Billet Oil Filter by Pure Power is truly the last oil filter you will ever need to buy. 
<ul>
  <li>Billet Aluminum Housing</li>
	<li>Stainless Steel Micro-Screen Filtration</li>
	<li>Embedded Neodymium Magnets</li>
	<li>Mil-spec Viton Seals</li>
	<li>Stainless Steel By-Pass Sealing Ball &amp; Spring</li>
	<li>U.S. Pat. No. 7,413,089 and U.S. Pat. Pending</li>
</ul></td>
<td width="10"></td>
<td width="386"><p align="center"><img alt="K&amp;N Reusable Oil Filter Unassembled" height="184" src="/images/SS-3002_unassembled.jpg" width="250" /><br /><img alt="K&amp;N Reusable Oil Filter" height="317" src="images/SS-3002.jpg" width="250" /><br />
				  K&amp;N Washable / Reusable Oil Filter</p></td>
                </tr></table></td>
            </tr>
            <tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr><td><hr /></td></tr>
<tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
            <tr>
           	  <td><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
              <tr><td colspan="3"><h2>K&amp;N Inline Fuel/Oil Filters</h2></td>
              </tr>
              <tr><td colspan="3">&nbsp;</td></tr>
              <tr><td width="386"><p align="center"><img alt="K&amp;N Inline Fuel/Oil Filters" height="196" src="images/inline-filters_250w.jpg" width="250" /><br />
				  K&amp;N Inline Fuel/Oil Filters</p></td>
                  <td width="10"></td>
                  <td width="584">K&amp;N inline fuel/oil filters are perfect for automotive racing applications. These filters can be used with a variety of oils and fuels including methanol. The filter material is made from stainless steel and the housing is made from anodized aluminum. [ <a href="inline-filters.htm" class="nav3">MORE</a> ]</td></tr></table></td>
            </tr>
          </table>
